				<wikidot:authorName>Dr Reach</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1779895</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>For some reason, I had a lingering suspicion that it was 087 (probably when the probe starting reporting it was in an empty space and receiving and unreachable call for help), then stopped thinking that was it, then finished it. While I wasn't particularly moved by this, it is a neat piece of writing and hard-sci-fi-ish enough to make me feel happy about it. Real happy. :D</p> <p>Upvoted.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
