					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So there I was minding my own business at 1:30AM staring at the bedroom ceiling when this gem of inspiration dropped on me. I should sleep-deprive myself more often.</p> <p>Just a quick shout out to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1414765&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1425220782" alt="Doctor Cimmerian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1414765)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" >Doctor Cimmerian</a></span> who really helped me temper this from it's first iteration.</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SPOILER&nbsp;ALERT!</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">INCOMING!</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h4><span>BASED ON:</span></h4> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-087" target="_blank">SCP-087 - The Stairwell &amp; Exploration Logs</a></p> <h4><span>CAST:</span></h4> <p><strong>Dr. ██████</strong> / Chief Technician Officer Isaac Miles<br /> <strong>D-Class</strong> / Probe-H9<br /> <strong>Crying Child</strong> / The SOS Signal<br /> <strong>SCP-087</strong> / The Spatial Anomaly (Quadrant-087)<br /> <strong>SCP-087-1</strong> / The Planetoid</p> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
